latestPosts.caption:
26 years since I was first introduced to this classical dance form called Kathak. It’s been a crazy enriching journey with the guidance, training & blessings of our Guru Late Smt. Asha Joglekar, आमच्या लाडक्या मावशी! 🌸🙏🏻

Performing at NCPA @ncpamumbai was a dream we saw as young girls learning Kathak, which we were fortunate enough to fulfil more than once! 

Only and only grateful to our parents, teachers, colleagues and all our well wishers to have always supported us in our endeavours.

Special thanks to @swapnokalpa2 ma’am for providing us such opportunities to showcase our art form at such a prestigious platform! 🙏🏻

I want to pour my heart out but falling short of words.

Finally, heartfelt gratitude to @parinitashah who’s seen it all with me since childhood. Felt really proud to be able to perform with not only her but also her students.
We learnt together, we dreamt together, we grew together and we performed together! 🧿 

To more such dreams getting fulfilled! 🙏🏻🌸
